I"€<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/systemd/system/&lt;$SERVICE_NAME&gt;.service</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>[Unit]
Description=&lt;$SERVICE_DESCRIPTION&gt;
   
[Service]
ExecStart=&lt;$SERVICE_COMMAND&gt;
   
[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Reload Systemd config:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl daemon-reload
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Enable &amp; start service:
    <div class="language-bash highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>systemctl <span class="nb">enable</span> <span class="nt">--now</span> &lt;<span class="nv">$SERVICE_NAME</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>.service
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
</ol>

